HEADWORD: Salver
<hw>Salv"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who salves, or
uses salve as a remedy; hence, a quacksalver, or quack.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

